channel.title: Help with server needed
channel.description:
Whenever I try to run server it comes up saying
Starting pimpscape Server on 0.0.0.0:43594
I have phonescape source and have compiled and everything but it doesn't run properly. Is there something with no-ip i have to do? or with a source file

item.title: Help with server needed
item.dc:creator: @Sir_roju Sir roju
item.description:
@Sir_roju wrote:

that starting … means your server is running on localhost atm…
but
if you want host it for public, then you should download no-ip update client, google it and if you are only login in localhost for testing your server, try log in with client that ip is setted to 127.0.0.1 and port 43594.
